operator Mike Rietveldt
submitter Bjorn Gustavsson
resources NI(10)
notes
HF-pumping of the ionosphere will be used to enhance optical emissions, create
ionospheric irregularities and increase the electron temperature in the F-region.
Quiet magnetospheric conditions with high enough critial frequency and for the
optical observations clear skies.
